text: Peyronnet is a French surname that may refer to *Albert Peyronnet (1862–1958), French politician *Jean-Claude Peyronnet (born 1940), French politician *Pierre-Denis, Comte de Peyronnet (1778–1884), French politician ==See also== *Le Clos du Peyronnet, an arts and crafts garden in Menton, France Category:French-language surnames
title: Peyronnet
